value.name: Mr. & Mrs. Smith
value.overview: Meet the Smiths: two lonely strangers, John and Jane, who have given up their lives and identities to be thrown together as partners – both in espionage and in marriage.

value.name: Mr. & Mrs. Smith
value.overview: Two globetrotting spies with different styles team up. Posing as husband and wife, they guard their true identities at all costs from the bad guys‒and from each other.
